  "description": "Svekolnik (or cold borscht) is a soup Artem’s grandma makes every summer in her dacha (summer house). This is not the same recipe but works great on hot summer days. It even feels almost like lemonade with the cold sweetness of beets and the gentle tickling of radishes.",
